<p>
<lb n="1"/>Āsīdvittēśavaṁśābdēḥ penuṁgoṁḍa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>purīśvaraḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmatpunuṁgosagōtrā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ryyō seṭṭinārāyaṇaprabhuḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tasya putrōbha
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vacchrīmān prōlāṁbāyā mahītalē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nīlise
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭṭīti vikhyātassaguṇāḍhyassuśīlavān <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="6"/>śrīśākābdē sunētrāṁgajaśararaja<unclear>nī</unclear>nātha
<lb n="7" break="no"/>prithvīprasaṁghē (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) phālguṇyāṁ śuklapakṣē
<lb n="8"/>prakaṭitajayatithyā marēśējyavārē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīma
<lb n="9" break="no"/><unclear>llē</unclear>śāya bhaktyā tribhuvanaviditāyādrikanyā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>dhipāya prādādācaṁdratāraṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> śa
<lb n="11"/>daśadiśaṁ dīpamatyujvalākhyaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> mallīśva
<lb n="12" break="no"/>radēvaraku nīliseṭṭi Iccina mōdālu 25
<lb n="13"/>vīniṁ jakoni nallaṁbrōlebōyini ko
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ḍuku bācenabōyuṁḍu nitya
<lb n="15"/>maneṁḍu neyyu naḍapaṁgalavāru tana
<lb n="16"/>putrānupavutramai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nīliseṭi dīpa
<lb n="17" break="no"/><unclear>mu</unclear> naṁdamallabōni koḍkuprōlebōyuṁḍu tavyaṁ
<lb n="18" break="no"/><unclear>ḍu</unclear> putrānupauvutra<unclear>ṁ</unclear> naḍapaṁgalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīrē maṟi<unclear>yu</unclear>
<lb n="19"/>Aradīpānaku nicina mōdalu 13 vīniṁ jēkoni kāpa
<lb n="20" break="no"/>bōyini koḍku kommanabōyuṁḍu nitya tavve
<lb n="21" break="no"/>ṁḍu neyyi naḍapaṁgalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

